# Critical Customer Touchpoints

The following touchpoints have the greatest impact on customer satisfaction:

### Website Experience

First impression.

---

### Initial Response Time

Builds trust.

---

### Consultation Quality

Determines conversion likelihood.

---

### Service Delivery

Core customer experience.

---

### Post-Service Follow-Up

