# Relationships

## Customer → Leads

One customer can create multiple leads.

Relationship:

One-to-Many

---

## Customer → Bookings

One customer can have multiple bookings.

Relationship:

One-to-Many

---

## Service → Leads

One service can be associated with many leads.

Relationship:

One-to-Many

---

## Service → Bookings

One service can have many bookings.

Relationship:

One-to-Many

---

## Package → Services

Packages can contain multiple services.

Relationship:

Many-to-Many

---

## User → Leads

Coordinators can manage multiple leads.

Relationship:

One-to-Many

---

## User → Bookings

Coordinators can manage multiple bookings.

Relationship:

One-to-Many

---

