# 10. Future Expansion Modules & Product Roadmap

## Introduction

The Moksha Gaya platform has been designed with long-term scalability in mind. While Version 1 focuses on lead generation, service management, and operational efficiency, the platform architecture should support future enhancements without requiring major redesigns.

This roadmap outlines the planned evolution of the platform over multiple development phases.

---

# Product Evolution Strategy

The platform will evolve through a phased development approach.

### Phase 1

Business Foundation

### Phase 2

Digital Operations

### Phase 3

Customer Self-Service

### Phase 4

Multi-City Expansion

### Phase 5

Global Spiritual Ecosystem

